  <h2 id="opportunity-attributes-1" class="govuk-heading-m app-summary-list-heading">Overview</h2>
  
  

  

  

  

  

  
<dl class="govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list app-govuk-summary-list--top-border govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Summary of the work
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          HMRC will conduct the research and provide the researchers discussion guides and any research materials needed. The recruitment agency is expected to:<br><br>- provide recruitment of users for research <br>- pay incentives to users taking part in research<br>- organisation of user participation and attendance on the day
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Location
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          London
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Research dates
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          Expected start date of contract mid/late April.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          Organisation the work is for
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          HM Revenue and Customs
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
